**figure of speech in which an expression is deliberately attributed to a different cause to conceal the original emotion**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   இலேசவணி
-


**figure of speech in which the natural outward expression of a certain real emotion in ones mind is deliberately attributed to quite a different cause or purpose to conceal the emotion altogether**
**சொற்குவை - அகரமுதலித் திட்ட இயக்ககம்**
- -   இலேசவணி
-


